         <COMPLEMENTARY_INFO>
            <INFO_ADD>
               <P>The Supplier Day format will be: the morning session (11:00 — 13:00) will involve a group session with all interested parties, where we will provide a more detailed description of the project and we expect to discuss about different approaches to the work and the main areas for investigation. We will then have an hour lunch break followed by an afternoon session (14:00-15:00) which will be divided up into a series of pre-booked one-to-one sessions between BEIS officials and potential contractors, to give organisations the opportunity to ask more detailed questions.</P>
